      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model and the Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model were selected based on published precedent for rotating blood-contacting devices. Formal model-form UQ is not required at this risk level."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
