    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at this model risk level with documented justification. The CFD model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The assessment team accepts the simulation evidence for the stated regulatory decision context.",
